<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <title></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-GLhlTQ8iRABdZLl6O3oVMWSktQOp6b7In1Zl3/Jr59b6EGGoI1aFkw7cmDA6j6gD" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style type="text/css">
		body {
			font-family: 'pfalfabeta', 'Aegithalos', Fallback, sans-serif;
		}

		@font-face {
    		font-family: Aegithalos;
    		src: url("/assets/fonts/aegithalos.otf") format("opentype");
		}

		@font-face {
    		font-family: 'pfalfabeta';
    		src: url('/assets/fonts/pfalfabeta/pfalfabeta-regular.otf') format('opentype');
    		font-weight: normal;
    		font-style: normal;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body contenteditable="true">
	<div class="container-fluid text-center">
		<div class="row mb-3">
			<div class="col-12 text-center">
				<!--<img src="/assets/img/logo_no_name.png" height="100"/>-->
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row mb-2">
			<div class="col text-end me-n">
				<h5 class="mb-0">Ψάρι ημέρας</h5>
				<p class="mb-1">Ρωτήστε μας για το φρέσκο ψάρι ημέρας</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-1"></div>
			<div class="col text-start ms-n">
				<h5 class="mb-0">Catch of the day</h5>
				<p class="mb-1">fresh local fish, different selection each day, ask for advice</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		{% for menuSection in menuSections %}
			{% for menuItem in menuSection.getActiveMenuItems %}
				<div class="row mb-2">
					<div class="col text-end me-n">
						<h5 class="mb-0">
							{{(menuItem.getTranslation('el').getName|split('/'))[0]}}
						</h5>
						<p class="mb-1">
							{{menuItem.getCustomField('print_menu_description_el')|nl2br}}
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="col-1">&euro;{{menuItem.getPrice}}</div>
					<div class="col text-start ms-n">
						<h5 class="mb-0">
							{{(menuItem.getTranslation('en').getName|split('/'))[0]}}
						</h5>
						<p class="mb-1">
							{{menuItem.getCustomField('print_menu_description_en')|nl2br}}
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			{% endfor %}
		{% endfor %}
		<div class="row mb-3">
			<div class="col-12 text-center">
				<p class="mb-1">
					{#{% for i in 1..10 %}
						<img width="50" src="/assets/img/fish_color.png"/>
					{% endfor %}#}
				</p>
				<p class="mb-1">
					Παρακαλούμε ενημερώστε το προσωπικό της επιχείρησης μας για τυχόν αλλεργίες ή δυσανεξίες που μπορεί να έχετε.<br/>
					Please let us know of any food allergies we should be aware of in the preparation of your meal.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>